file.name: issue4808.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Issue 11242 - exploded query params
  description: "Exploded query params"
  version: "1.0.0"
servers:
  - url: localhost:8080
paths:
  /api:
    get:
      operationId: GetSomeValue
      parameters:
      - in: query
        name: QueryObject
        explode: true
        style: form
        schema:
          type: object
          properties:
            since:
              type: string
            sinceBuild:
              type: string
            maxBuilds:
              type: integer
            maxWaitSecs:
              type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Some return value
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SomeReturnValue'
              example:
                someValue: value
components:
  schemas:
    SomeReturnValue:
      type: object
      required:
        - someValue
      properties:
        someValue:
          type: string
